dise must be in its original, unused condition unless there is a manufacturer's defect; and<p></li><li><p>The merchandise must be accompanied by either the original Dillard's Receipt or the original Dillard's Proof of Purchase Label. (Proof of Purchase information is included on the packing slip for all Dillard's Direct orders.)<p></li></ol></p><p class="answer">For orders placed using PayPal®, refunds will be issued in the form of a Dillard’s Gift Card.</p><p class="answer">All merchandise tags should remain attached.</p><p class="answer"><strong><u>Follow these instructions to send return back</u></strong></p><p class="answer">We recommend that you insure the package and ship via a traceable method. Dillard's offer's a Fed Ex return label you can print from your computer and attach to the return package.</p><ol><li><p>Re-pack your returns along with your receipt. You may use the original box.<p></li><li><p>Affix the return label to the box. Be sure to cover or remove any previous labels. You will be charged $6.95 for use of the return label.<p></li><li><p>Drop your return at any USPS (U.S. Mail) location.<p></li></ol><p class="answer">Your refund should process within 7-10 business days after shipment.</p><p class="answer">No refunds are given on shipping and handling charges. Personalized items and clearance items marked down 65% or more cannot be returned.</p><p class="answer"><strong><u>Gift Return?</u></strong></p><p class="answer">The merchandise may be mailed back to us or returned to any Dillard's location. You will be responsible for the shipping fees. If the merchandise being returned was purchased using a credit card and we credit your account, the credit will show on the statement you receive after the issuing bank applies the credit.</p><p class="answer">If you exchange merchandise, your account will be credited for the return and a sale rung for the new merchandise.</p><p class="answer">Address package to:</p><p class="answer">Dillard's</p><p class="answer">600 Carnahan Drive</p><p class="answer">Maumelle, AR 72113</p></div></div></div><!---------------------------------------------- Pricing Policy ----------------------------------------------><div class="info-block"><div class="col-xs-12"><h3 class="info-block-title" id="policies-notices-question-pricing">Pricing Policy</h3><div class="info-block-body"><p class="answer">Dillard's is committed to offering quality merchandise at fair, competitive prices. In most cases, the Internet prices will reflect store prices. However, there may be some exceptions. Internet sale prices expire at midnight Central time on the date displayed for the item. Prices and sales are subject to change without notice.</p><p class="answer">Dillard's does not make price adjustments.</p><p class="answer">Merchandise available through Dillards.com may not be available in all our stores.</p></div></div></div><!---------------------------------------------- Shipping Policy -------------------------------------------><div class="info-block"><div class="col-xs-12"><h3 class="info-block-title" id="policies-notices-question-shipping">Shipping Policy</h3><div class="info-block-body"><p class="answer">Our service providers are FedEx and USPS. The carrier is determined by the service available for your <q>ship to</q> location and the method of delivery (Standard, Expedited or Next Business Day) you select. Delivery times do not include processing time. Processing time for in stock items is approximately two (2) business days.</p><p class="answer">If the item is <u>not</u> in stock, you will receive an email to notify you. When your order ships, you will receive an email that includes the name of the carrier and a tracking number. You will also receive an email when your purchase has been delivered.</p><p class="answer">Standard delivery time is two (2) to five (5) business days after shipping. Orders requesting Expedited service or Next Business Day service, and ordered prior to 12:00 pm (noon) central time, are shipped the same day (Monday through Friday). Expedited or Next Business Day orders placed on Friday after 12:00 pm (noon) central time, Saturday, Sunday or a Holiday will be shipped the following business day. You can expect delivery in two (2) business days for Expedited service and one (1) business day for Next Business Day service after shipping.</p><p class="answer">Additional charges will be applied to merchandise shipped to Alaska, Hawaii, and U.S. Territories.</p><p class="answer">Please allow two (2) to eight (8) weeks for delivery to APO/FPO addresses. However, due to restrictions at APO/FPO postal facilities, we are unable to ship oversized and/or heavy items to APO/FPO addresses. Expedited shipping and Next Business Day shipping are not available for P.O. Box, APO/FPO addresses, Alaska, Hawaii, or U.S.Territories.</p><p class="answer">Shipping charges are calculated for each address and are based on the order amount being shipped to that address.</p><p class="answer">The following charges will apply to your order:</p><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8"><table class="table"><caption><strong>CONTINENTAL <abbr class="initialism">U.S.</abbr></strong></caption><thead><tr><th>ORDER AMOUNT</th><th>STANDARD</th><th>EXPEDITED</th><th>Next Business Day</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Up to $149.99</td><td>$9.95</td><td>$20.00</td><td>$30.00</td></tr><tr><td>$150.00 and Up</td><td>Free*</td><td>$20.00</td><td>$30.00</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8"><table class="table"><caption><strong>CONTINENTAL <abbr class="initialism">U.S.-P.O.</abbr><abbr class="initialism">BOX</abbr>/ <abbr class="initialism">APO</abbr>/ <abbr class="initialism">FPO</abbr></strong></caption><thead><tr><th>ORDER AMOUNT</th><th>STANDARD</th><th>EXPEDITED</th><th>Next Business Day</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Up to $149.99</td><td>$9.95</td><td>Not Available</td><td>Not Avail